NOTES

3 things needed: 
	-scene 
	-camera
	-rednerer

Perspective Camera takes a few parameters: FOV, Aspect, Near, Far, XYZ coordinates 

scene is what you're viewing what you have obj in-- what the user will see the world through

perspective camera allows you to have depth

parameters for camera: FOV (extent of the scene that's on display at a given moment) in degrees, aspect ratio, near and far clipping plane

MeshBasicMaterial not effected by light 
Different types of materials: Phong, Lambert